{"tid":227192,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(郭文貴事件)美國之音已經演變成共產黨和中國之聲","createTime":"2017-05-03T04:01:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-08T10:41:04.000Z","uid":100986,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fde17b0ef79eea3110a98610395ddfa1dddb7a65","tid":227192,"uid":100986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T04:01:32.000Z","msg":"(郭文貴事件)美國之音已經演變成共產黨和中國之聲<br />\n<br />\n余杰<br />\n<strong>美國之音正在演變成德國之聲，成為共產黨的編外媒體。當年，克林頓傲慢地說，中共控制網路時代的媒體，如同要將果凍釘在墻上。如今，美國之音被中共像果凍一樣釘在墻上了。<br />\n多年前，我就發現美國之音被共產黨滲透嚴重，有一次參加美國之音記者編輯的派對，耳邊聽到的全是咒罵美國和讚美中國的聲音，宛如身處環球時報編輯部。<br />\n可惜，美國FBI/CIA對此嚴重情況熟視無睹。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/yujie1989/posts/697291833787053\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fyujie1989%2Fposts%2F697291833787053&d=t9lvrop9ljT%2F%2Fon6qZ%2B%2Fxtr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=2b31b3d3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/yujie1989/posts/697291833787053</a><br />\n<br />\n郭文貴：達賴喇嘛尊者是我的朋友（組圖）<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.bannedbook.org/bnews/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/guowengui21.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bannedbook.org%2Fbnews%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F03%2Fguowengui21.gif&h=1ad9060a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/C6QO_BeVUAANde3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FC6QO_BeVUAANde3.jpg&h=8a526d8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.huaglad.com/zh-tw/lovecn/20170307/296673.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.huaglad.com%2Fzh-tw%2Flovecn%2F20170307%2F296673.html&d=t9lvrop9ljT%2F%2Fon6qZ%2B%2Fxtr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=26123833\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.huaglad.com/zh-tw/lovecn/20170307/296673.html</a>"},{"pid":"30c99ede41574be85584cc4a72ebeb4d7f704137","tid":227192,"uid":100986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T04:07:08.000Z","msg":"Yi Sulaiman Gu<br />\n記者東方發推，一線團隊全部被停職調查。這種方式的調查，主持者、對象和目的很可疑。<br />\n<br />\n余杰<br />\n張晶偏偏若無其事。<br />\n<br />\nNaike Lu<br />\n該有事終會出事，​​等著瞧吧。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/yujie1989/posts/697291833787053\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fyujie1989%2Fposts%2F697291833787053&d=t9lvrop9ljT%2F%2Fon6qZ%2B%2Fxtr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=2b31b3d3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/yujie1989/posts/697291833787053</a>"},{"pid":"81f40be410e2b4877b94757b7d77fe799382ae61","tid":227192,"uid":100986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T04:11:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/C6QO_BeVAAA8akD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FC6QO_BeVAAA8akD.jpg&h=6ba5ce17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/C6QO_BdU4AAKURL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FC6QO_BdU4AAKURL.jpg&h=edd3935b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b5380e01c41b2fd82b0ca01fba171bcfcf28b15a","tid":227192,"uid":71826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T04:18:14.000Z","msg":"第一張咁似key圖"},{"pid":"789eab57bfa90883354b4923e099a9fddbbd88fe","tid":227192,"uid":100986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T04:33:42.000Z","msg":"孔金坤 <br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\"><strong>很顯然後現代主義徹底解構下所形成的所謂現代極端自由主義社會，在這波鬥爭中鬥輸了中國共產黨，共產病毒當然侵入，繁殖，滲透，先是後現代主義的起源地歐洲，再來美國，到現在已經全世界化。 <br />\n美國之音共產黨化，是結果，不是原因，是極端自由主義所型構成之什麼都可以，什麼都無所謂的不設防社會條件下，才使共產黨如入無人之地，快速漫延所產生的結果。 </strong></span><br />\n川普在這波仍在進行中的鬥爭潮中串出，是一個值得留意的事件，不在於他是美國總統，而是在極端自由主義潰敗的情況下，這股力量是否能夠阻擋共產世界的狂潮。 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/yujie1989/posts/697291833787053\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fyujie1989%2Fposts%2F697291833787053&d=t9lvrop9ljT%2F%2Fon6qZ%2B%2Fxtr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=2b31b3d3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/yujie1989/posts/697291833787053</a>"},{"pid":"7f88d70d1998f92c06812e88cb515f13f1b64d70","tid":227192,"uid":100986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T04:59:27.000Z","msg":"本土人同兩登仔2011年日講夜講既常識(中國人和新香港人殖民香港, 支資買起香港), 竟然要由一個美國人(郭文貴)黎講<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"829da2f63b34a396693f355cbd675efaf129347b","tid":227192,"uid":100986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T04:59:51.000Z","msg":"本土人同兩登仔2011年<strong>起</strong>日講夜講既常識(中國人和新香港人殖民香港, 支資買起香港), 竟然要由一個美國人(郭文貴)黎講<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c953863ec4484d0a8eca98ed1865cdc0223c5684","tid":227192,"uid":100986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T06:53:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.thetibetpost.com/images/stories/August2011/18thaugust2011tpiestonia2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thetibetpost.com%2Fimages%2Fstories%2FAugust2011%2F18thaugust2011tpiestonia2.jpg&h=898e7d28&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cefdc55118e023aeef0bb85e088edef924dd2c92","tid":227192,"uid":100986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T07:11:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>第一張咁似key圖</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 邊忽似"},{"pid":"2406d0750a011739afde07c50625c4a40e024d5c","tid":227192,"uid":100986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T07:54:36.000Z","msg":"發達啦巴打話冇黎呢度<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/03.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98e60c747574e4a8274630bfae0a18a60716406d","tid":227192,"uid":100986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T16:40:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>發達啦巴打話冇黎呢度<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/03.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />2011年起就已經有睇發達啦巴打既鄭立(雖然唔係完全同意曬鄭立)post和講台灣既post<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gi